	<longdescription>
		Kazam is a simple screen recording program that will capture the content
		of your screen and record a video file that can be played by any video player
		that supports VP8/WebM video format. Kazam has been designed with simplicity
		in mind and provides a clean, intuitive interface. It can record the entire
		desktop or just a selected area, and includes audio recording capabilities.

		This version (Kazam2) includes enhanced features like OCR (Optical Character
		Recognition), AI integration, broadcasting capabilities, and improved capture
		functionality compared to the original Kazam.
	</longdescription>
